{"type": "article", "id": 2634, "title": "为每种食物打造的专属餐具", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-29T08:42:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232335NTo7tyrAeDCa5Llx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t如果你家厨房的餐具还是以筷子、勺子、叉子等这样的传统功能分类的话，可以来看看以色列设计师 Lee Ben David 令人大开眼界的新型分类方法，它大抵是想给每一种食物都设计一种适合用餐者食用的专属餐具，所以就有了下面这些专门食用朝鲜蓟，意大利面，沙拉和毛豆的不锈钢餐具。Lee Ben David 表示：“我们使用的餐具是作为我们身体的延伸，避免我们的双手直接接触到食物，这是最本能的需求之一。”\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232332jnwPvGgk71QKzV2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232333NMf8dcyY0kgT3Kn6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232333robz4IXlhNZTHtOw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232334ai1n4V2pZor5GXWq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}